tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE collections (
    collection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    collection_name VARCHAR(255),
    collection_year INT,
    designer_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (designer_id) REFERENCES designers(designer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE collections (
    collection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    collection_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    designer_id INT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_designer_id
        FOREIGN KEY (designer_id)
        REFERENCES designers(designer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    collaboration_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    designer_id INT,
    collection_id INT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_designer_id
        FOREIGN KEY (designer_id)
        REFERENCES designers(designer_id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_collection_id
        FOREIGN KEY (collection_id)
        REFERENCES collections(collection_id)
);

CREATE TABLE `collections` (
  `collection_id` INT PRIMARY KEY,
  `name` VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  `year` INT,
  `designer_id` INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (designer_id) REFERENCES designers(designer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE `collaborations` (
  `collaboration_id` INT PRIMARY KEY,
  `designer_id` INT,
  `partner_id` INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (designer_id) REFERENCES designers(designer_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (partner_id) REFERENCES designers(designer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE collections (
  collection_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  collection_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  collection_year INT,
  designer_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (designer_id) REFERENCES fashion_designers (designer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE designer_collections (
  designer_id INT,
  collection_id INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (designer_id, collection_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (designer_id) REFERENCES fashion_designers (designer_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (collection_id) REFERENCES collections (collection_id)
);

CREATE TABLE designer_collaborations (
  designer_id INT,
  collaboration_id INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (designer_id, collaboration_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (designer_id) REFERENCES fashion_designers (designer_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (collaboration_id) REFERENCES collaboration_partners (collaboration_id)
);
